data.description: The first floor has a bright open concept kitchen, dining and living room with a privately enclosed patio area and half bath. Upstairs, the spacious master suite features a twin vanity and walk-in closet. Second story also includes an additional full bath, two bedrooms, utility closet and plenty of storage. Interior selections include 36'' cabinets, granite kitchen countertops, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, and energy saving features. Storage is not an issue here, this townhome features an over-sized single car garage.
